      "timestamp": "2025-12-10T12:50:41.223+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "I'm generally of the opinion that things should be `-Werror`, I dislike it when things warn -- either it should be important enough I care about and thus an error or it isn't important and thus shouldn't be produced.",
