      "content": "I would trust klayout.  I'm trying to determine if the PPLUS/NPLUS spacing error is real or not, but as usual the problem is trying to understand the garbled mess that is the rule documentation.  In all likelihood I implemented the spacing rule as I understood it, which may or may not be how it is actually implemented by GF.",
